OL,3,CLandlord fined #14k after exposing
OL,4,Ctenants to 'risk of serious harm'
OL,6,FA landlord has been ordered to pay
OL,7,F#14,000 after pleading guilty to
OL,8,Fexposing his tenants to "the risk of
OL,9,Fserious harm."
OL,11,FNeil McCann, 58, received the fine
OL,12,Fafter he left his tenants in Bootle
OL,13,Fwith no working smoke detectors, no
OL,14,Ffixed heating, no electrical supply to
OL,15,Fone of the flats and no front door.
OL,17,FMcCann appeared for sentencing at
OL,18,FSefton Magistrates court in Bootle
OL,19,Fafter ignoring safety risks and
OL,20,Fcontinuing to allow tenants to live in
OL,21,Fdangerous conditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
