OL,3,CLandlord fined #14k after exposing
OL,4,Ctenants to 'risk of serious harm'
OL,6,FThe private landlord rents out four
OL,7,Fflats at a property on Alexandra Road
OL,8,Fin Crosby.
OL,10,FThe court heard one of the tenants
OL,11,Fsubmitted a complaint to Sefton
OL,12,FCouncil in October 2023, which then
OL,13,Finitiated an inspection of the house.
OL,15,FAs a result, McCann was served a
OL,16,Fschedule of works, including guidance
OL,17,Fon what improvements were needed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
