OL,4,Ctenants to 'risk of serious harm'
OL,6,FA further inspection in October 2024
OL,7,Fconfirmed that McCann had not only
OL,8,Ffailed to start on those improvements,
OL,9,Fbut the condition of the property had
OL,10,Fdeteriorated.
OL,12,FFollowing the 2024 visit, officers
OL,13,Fserved an improvement notice for the
OL,14,Fbuilding and advised McCann to address
OL,15,Fidentified hazards such as a lack of
OL,16,Ffire protection, excess cold,
OL,17,Fstructural collapse and damp and mould.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
