OL,6,FThe improvement notice meant McCann
OL,7,Fhad until 8 November 2024 to start
OL,8,Fimprovement work, and he was required
OL,9,Fto complete them by 8 January 2025.
OL,11,FOn 28 January 2025, the council re-
OL,12,Finspected the property and found that
OL,13,Fone of the flats remained occupied,
OL,14,Fand none of the works listed in the
OL,15,Fimprovement notice had been carried
OL,16,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
