OL,3,CLandlord fined #14k after exposing
OL,4,Ctenants to 'risk of serious harm'
OL,6,FA Sefton council spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"At this time our diligent officers
OL,8,Fdeemed there to be an imminent risk of
OL,9,Fserious harm to the health and safety
OL,10,Fof anyone living in or visiting one of
OL,11,Fthe flats.
OL,13,F"We immediately served an emergency
OL,14,Fprohibition order on this flat,
OL,15,Fprohibiting it from being used as
OL,16,Fresidential accommodation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
