OL,3,CLandlord fined #14k after exposing
OL,4,Ctenants to 'risk of serious harm'
OL,6,FThe prohibition order meant McCann had
OL,7,Fto vacate the tenant, who would be
OL,8,Feligible for housing support from the
OL,9,Flocal authority. However, inspectors
OL,10,Ffound the tenant had remained in the
OL,11,Fflat.
OL,13,FSumming up the offences, the
OL,14,Fmagistrate acknowledged the difficulty
OL,15,FMcCann had with one of his tenants,
OL,16,Fbut said this should not have
OL,17,Fprevented him from satisfying his
OL,18,Fstatutory duties.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
