OL,3,CLandlord fined #14k after exposing
OL,4,Ctenants to 'risk of serious harm'
OL,6,FThe court heard McCann has now
OL,7,Fstarted, and in some cases finished,
OL,8,Fworks at the Alexandra Road property.
OL,10,FHowever, he was fined #7,000 for the
OL,11,Fbreach of the improvement notice,
OL,12,F#7,000 for breaching the prohibition
OL,13,Fnotice, and was ordered to pay the
OL,14,Flegal costs.
OL,16,FThe Sefton Council spokesperson added:
OL,17,F"We will always act to protect our
OL,18,Fcommunities, including tenants who are
OL,19,Fliving in awful conditions which are
OL,20,Fsimply not safe.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
